description:
Below Deck - Season 3, Preview Special




Don't Miss the Boat

Captain Lee and his returning crew - Kate, Eddie and Amy are joined by five new crew members as they embark on a new charter season in the Bahamas aboard the 161' luxury yacht Eros. A new boat, new guests, high demands, and close quarters will bring these yachties to the boiling point.




Original Air Date: 04-Aug-2015
